"`scuv install 3.12` runs `uv python install 3.12` internally. uv downloads a "
"standalone Python build from the [python-build-standalone](https://"
"github.com/indygreg/python-build-standalone) project and stores it in "
"`~/.local/share/uv/python/`."
msgstr ""
