msgstr "동일한 환경"

#: src/commands/diff.md:69
msgid "Mixed differences"
msgstr "여러 차이 혼재"

#: src/commands/diff.md:89
msgid ""
"The `~` marker flags changed scalar fields; `-`/`+` flag removed/added "
